jsx.client
Class Client

java.lang.Object
  js.Disposable
      jsx.client.Global
          jsx.client.Client
Direct Known Subclasses:
Win
public abstract class Client
extends Global

A utility class accessing the global objects and functions of JavaScript with a full client-side support.

Users are encouraged to use the utilities and static fields provided in this class instead of the opaque methods and the members of the JsGlobal class or the JsClient class in consideration of the reuse benefit for re-compilation results.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
